y, P.L., Soter, S., (1979) Icarus, 40 (1), p. 1; Zook, H.A., Berg, O.E., (1975) Planet. Space Sci., 23 (1), p. 183; Grün, E., (1995) Planet. Space Sci., 43 (8), p. 953; Wehry, A., Mann, I., (1999) Astron. Astrophys., 341, p. 296; Vaisberg, O.L., Smirnov, V., Omelchenko, A., Gorn, L., Iovlev, M., (1987) Astron. Astrophys., 187, p. 753; Mazets, E.P., (1987) Astron. Astrophys., 187, p. 699; Rickman, H., (1998) Solar System Ices, p. 395. , Dordrecht: Kluwer; Marconi, M., Mendis, D., (1981) Astrophys. J., 260, p. 386; Popel, S.I., Gisko, A.A., (2006) Nonlinear Processes Geophys., 13 (2), p. 223; Newburn, R.L., Spinard, H., (1989) Astron. J., 97, p. 552; Singh, P.D., De Almeida, A.A., Huebner, W.F., (1992) Astron. J., 104, p. 848; Storrs, A.D., Cochran, A.L., Barker, E.S., (1992) Icarus, 98 (2), p. 163; Losseva, T.V., Golub'A, P., Kosarev, I.B., Popel, S.I., Nemtchinov, I.V., (2002) Proc. Conf. on Asteroids, Comets, Meteors-ACM2002, p. 873. , (Berlin, 29 July-2 August 2002) (European Space Agency); Denysenko, I.B., Ostrikov, K., Xu, S., Yu, M.Y., Diong, C.H., (2003) J. Appl. Phys., 94 (9), p. 6097; Nakamura, Y., Bailung, H., Shukla, P.K., (1999) Phys. Rev. Lett., 83 (8), p. 1602; Luo, Q.-Z., D'Angelo, N., Merlino, R.L., (1999) Phys. Plasmas, 6 (9), p. 3455; Popel, S.I., Yu, M.Y., Tsytovich, V.N., (1996) Phys. Plasmas, 3 (12), p. 4313; Popel, S.I., Gisko, A.A., Golub'A, P., Losseva, T.V., Bingham, R., Shukla, P.K., (2000) Phys. Plasmas, 7 (6), p. 2410; Link, H., Leinert, C., Pitz, E., Salm, N., (1976) Interplanetary Dust and Zodiacal Light, p. 113. , Berlin: Springer; Yu, M.Y., Luo, H., (1995) Phys. Plasmas, 2 (3), p. 591; Ma, J.X., Yu, M.Y., Liang, X.P., Zheng, J., Liu, W.D., Yu, C.X., (2002) Phys. Plasmas, 9 (5), p. 1584; Kopnin, S.I., Kosarev, I.N., Popel, S.I., Yu, M.Y., (2004) Planet. Space Sci., 52 (13), p. 1187; W-G, Z., Ma, J.X., Y-R, L., Y-B, Z., Y-H, C., (2010) Planet. Space Sci., 58 (5), p. 801; Ostrikov, K., Denysenko, I.B., Vladimirov, S.V., Xu, S., Sugai, H.,